[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     94[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     95[0m:[38;5;10m[49m The safety layer is properly implemented:
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     96[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - **Trial stopped:** Checked in both `update_posteriors` (rejects further learning) and `randomize_patient` (rejects new enrollments). Raises clear exceptions.
